about: Bar - Dancing - Bisto at the Westergasfabriek Amsterdam. The best place to Rock & Roll in Amsterdam. Hoka Hey!
description: Pacific Parc is a bar - dancing - bistro at the Westergasfabriek Amsterdam. Come round for coffee, lunch, our sunny terrace (if it is not raining in Holland), casual dinner and of course crazy late nights with amsterdams sleaziest diskjocks, live rock & roll and happy drinking and dancing times.
name: Pacific Parc
